Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_win_wr_addr

NPEI_WIN_WR_ADDR = NPEI Window Write Address Register

Contains the address to be writen to when a write operation is started by writing the NPEI_WIN_WR_DATA register (see below).

Notes: Even though address bit [2] can be set, it should always be kept to '0'.
